headline.main: Malaysia Expels North Korean Envoy After Kim Jong Nam Murder
headline.print_headline: Malaysia Expels North Korean Envoy After Kim Jong Nam Murder

lead_paragraph: Malaysia said on Saturday it was expelling the North Korean ambassador, escalating a diplomatic row between the two countries over the murder of the estranged half-brother of North Korean leader Kim Jong Un.
